
IoTrain-Sim v1.0
----------------
* Added C files with solutions for most of the exercises, so that
  learners can verify by themselves their answers
* Did a full revision of the training content to improve explanations,
  structure and file organization
* Added a graphical user interface (GUI) as the default interface for
  interacting with the program
* Added command-line arguments to control which user interface is
  used: the new GUI (default) or the legacy CLI
* Various minor bug fixes and improvements

IoTrain-Sim v0.1
----------------
* First public release, which includes training content for
  fundamental and security training